A man was shot on the head when he allegedly tried to hijack a police vehicle in Alberton on Monday afternoon.He was shot while trying to drive away with the car on the N3, police sources told News24.&nbsp;ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring said the car veered off the road during a shootout between police and the would-be hijacker.&nbsp;The police officer who was in the car sustained minor injuries.The man was taken to a nearby hospital. A second person was also arrested.&nbsp;http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/man-tries-to-hijack-police-car-on-n3-gets-shot-20170515